[I] A small vi/ex terminal text editor

[T] Nextvi is a modern clone of the command-line text editor vi(1), initially
[T] developed by Bill Joy in 1976 for Unix-based systems.

[U] https://github.com/kyx0r/nextvi

[A] kyx0r
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/editor
[F] CROSS

[L] OpenSource
[V] 5.0

[D] ce6bbf19f697455b31dffcadcd8849e580e569227976676e8785e7be nextvi-5.0.tar.gz https://github.com/kyx0r/nextvi/archive/5.0/

